<p>World Builder utilizes the Tron blockchain. You can use the <a href = "https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tronlink%EF%BC%88%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%9D%E9%92%B1%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%89/ibnejdfjmmkpcnlpebklmnkoeoihofec?hl=en-US">TronLink Chrome/Brave extension</a> if you're accessing this site on a desktop or laptop, or <a href = "https://mathwallet.org/cn/">Math Wallet</a> if you're on a mobile device.</p>
<p>We recommend using <a href = "https://brave.com/wor213">Brave web browser</a>. Brave rewards users for viewing ads, makes it easy to tip website content creators, and has security and privacy in mind, with local storage of user information, and Tor built in.</p>
<p>If you're interested in photography or art, and are tired of a certain other social media platform that happens to rhyme with gram, then check out <a href = "https://www.belacam.com/ref/alc_anthro">Belacam</a> and <a href = "https://www.publish0x.com/the-bcu-times/whats-belacam-and-bela-xrngpv?a=olejYD5djN&tid=worldbuilder">BELA</a>.</p> 